lead_paragraph: Ryan Moore, playing for only the third time in 10 weeks, shot a three-under 67 Thursday, sharing the lead with Eric Axley and Mathew Goggin at the EDS Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex. Only 24 of the 156 players in the field broke par in the first round played on the redesigned TPC Four Seasons course.
